    function resendConfirmMail(_uuid){
        jQuery.ajax({
            url: "https://hub.abinteractive.net/resend-mail",
            data: {
                uuid: _uuid
            },
            dataType: "json",
            method : "POST",
            error: function (_res){
                swal.fire("Error","Failed to complete request.","error");
            },
            success: function(_res){
                if(_res.success){
                    swal.fire("Request processed",_res.responseMessage,"success").then(function(){
                        if(_res.goToUrl){
                            window.location = _res.goToUrl;
                        }
                    });
                }else{
                    swal.fire("Error",_res.responseMessage,"error");
                }
            }
        });
    }
</script>
